    "We test two different tools for this operation: edspdf and pdfbox.",
    "Second, we evaluate three methods for detecting dates and target entities in texts: a rule-based method, a machine learning method, and a hybrid method (step 2).",
    "Finally, we replace these entities by plausible substitutes, to obtain a pseudonymized document (step 3).",
    "The types of identifying characteristics that we considered are listed at ►Table 1.",
    "We selected a set of EHRs split between training, development, and test sets."
